&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Product and Engineering to bring new subscription offers and value propositions to our audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive initiatives to improve the user journey from prospect to subscriber, focusing on seamless onboarding and friction reduction.&lt;/li&gt;
